  "original_title": "\u2018\u2018\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dc4\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 - \u0d85\u0d9c\u0db8\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc4\u0daf\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\u2018\u2018",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\"Pohottuwa is trying to get both the President and the Prime Minister\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The chief organizer of the opposition, Member of Parliament Mr. Lakshman Kiriella said in Colombo today (15) that the government is working to lead the country by kicking the aspirations of the people and appointing a president and a prime minister.",
        "Mr. Kiriella also mentioned that although Samagi Jana Balawega worked to win the aspirations of the people by forming an all-party government with all the parties in the parliament on the advice of religious leaders including Trinitarian prelates, a serious situation has arisen due to the government not agreeing to it.",
        "He said this in a press conference called at the opposition leader's office in Marx Fernando Mawatha, Colombo, that yesterday's agreement with the political parties to build the country by sharing the positions of the president and prime minister and the government and the opposition has broken down.",
        "Mr. Kiriella also mentioned that the opposition parties had reached an agreement on this matter in the last few days and had planned to inform the Speaker of this decision today, but at the last moment the position of some people changed and this confused situation has arisen."
      ],
